        }

        a {
            text-decoration: unset;
        }

        .header_sin_acceso {
            background: #002A8D;
            width: 100%;
            height: 64px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
            align-items: center;

            position: fixed;
            z-index: 1;
            top: 0;
            margin: auto;
        }

        .informacion {
            padding-top: 64px;
        }

        .informacion,
        .titulo_producto,
        .productos,
        .footer {
            margin: auto;
            text-align: center;
        }


        @media (min-width:1px) and (max-width:1279px) {
            .logo {
                margin-left: 16px;
            }

            .banca {
                margin-left: auto;
                margin-right: 16px;
            }

            .abre {
                display: none;
            }

            .desktop {
                display: none;
            }

            .mobile {
                display: block;
            }

            .productos {
                display: flex;
                justify-content: center;
                flex-wrap: wrap;
                width: 345px;
            }

            .titulo_producto {
                margin-top: 48px;
            }

        }

        @media (min-width:1280px) {
            .desktop {
                display: block;
            }

            .mobile {
                display: none;
            }


            .logo {
                margin-left: 116px;
                cursor: pointer;
            }

            .banca {
                margin-left: auto;
                width: 192px;
                height: 40px;
                margin-right: 12px;
                background-color: #ff7800;
                border-radius: 8px;
                display: flex;
                justify-content: center;
                align-items: center;
                cursor: pointer;
            }

            .banca:hover {
                background-color: #ff9333;
                transition: linear 200ms;
            }

            .abre {
                width: 164px;
                height: 40px;
                background-color: transparent;
                border-radius: 8px;
                border-style: solid;
                border-width: 1px;
                border-color: #fff;
                display: flex;
                justify-content: center;
                align-items: center;
                cursor: pointer;
                margin-right: 116px;
            }

            .abre:hover {
                transition: linear 200ms;
                background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, .3);
            }



            .informacion,
            .titulo_producto,
            .productos,
            .footer {
                width: 1440px;
                margin: auto;
                text-align: center;
            }
        }
    </style>
